channel.title: Cani delete
channel.description: can i delete a object such as an original table, what is the code for it ? or just some help will do, how do i change the spawn place when a player dies...

item.title: Cani delete
item.dc:creator: @Busta_Blader Busta Blader
item.description:
@Busta_Blader wrote:

the starting place?

If so go to player.java and search for “// initial x and y coordinates of the player”, or “teleportToX =”

change that and thats how you change the starting place when they log in.

Second part changing the spawn area when you die:

http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,261048.0.html

item.title: Cani delete
item.dc:creator: @Busta_Blader Busta Blader
item.description:
@Busta_Blader wrote:

yes you can, go to client.java and search for

“public void DeleteObjects” or “DeleteObjects”

There will be something like a whole heap of “deletethatobject(xxxx, xxxx)” (xxxx = coords)

copy one and change the xxxx to the x and y coords of the table
